## Environment Variable Reference

All env vars consumed by the API. These must be set in `/opt/lumiverb/.env` (Docker Compose reads it automatically when the compose file is in the same directory).

| Variable | Required | Description |
|----------|----------|-------------|
| `POSTGRES_PASSWORD` | Yes | Postgres `app` user password. Used in `CONTROL_PLANE_DATABASE_URL`. |
| `ADMIN_KEY` | Yes | Bearer token for `/v1/admin/*` routes. Keep private; used to provision tenants. |
| `CONTROL_PLANE_DATABASE_URL` | Derived | Set in compose from `POSTGRES_PASSWORD`. Override only if using an external Postgres. |
| `QUICKWIT_URL` | Derived | Set in compose to `http://quickwit:7280`. Override if using an external Quickwit. |
| `DATA_DIR` | Derived | Set in compose to `/data/storage` (Docker volume path). Override only if changing storage backend. |

